Package com.vincentdao.List

Class List<T extends Comparable<T>>

java.lang.Object
com.vincentdao.List.List<T>
Direct Known Subclasses:
LinkedList
public abstract class List<T extends Comparable<T>> extends Object

Abstract class List that holds all basic functions of a List.This is also applicable for its family, such as SinglyLinkedList, DoublyLinkedList, etc...

This abstract class can also be used for other ADT as well, such as Stack, Queue, Dequeue, etc...

Version:
0.1
Author:
vincentdao
